  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/ecfad98bec450e42adb13423e3ed3e25.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/ecfad98bec450e42adb13423e3ed3e25.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cuteness is optional. Strategy is a must. Cats Go is a 4-player co-op action game that blends tower defense, shooting, strategy, and... cats! Armed with plant-powered towers, your feline squad is ready to defend the village! Team up, build your strategy, and work together to expose the mysterious demon cat hiding among you. ■ This is NOT your typical tower defense game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ This is NOT your typical tower defense game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>[ Don’t be fooled by the cuteness ]</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your village using plant towers installed by cats themselves. A purr-fect blend of shooting action and tower defense gameplay! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>[ A suspicious cat? The Demon Mode is here! ]</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An evil cat is pretending to be a teammate and sneaking through the village. Sniff out the suspicious kitty and vote them out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><u>[ Supports 1–4 Players (Online Co-op & Local Multiplayer) ]</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Team up with friends, build your leafy towers, and defend together! Running low on meat? Time to call in a friend boost! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>[ Tons of Maps & Challenges Await ]</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > New maps, new plans—every match is a fresh challenge! Dive into the purr-fect world of strategic cat defense, whether you're a newbie or a master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/374f4e9490bccfb2b598e3d7680037c1.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/374f4e9490bccfb2b598e3d7680037c1.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/be1fdb0cd0de0c1f2a052db0a25a0adc.poster.avif?t=1754736393\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/be1fdb0cd0de0c1f2a052db0a25a0adc.webm?t=1754736393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ <u><strong>Solo Mode</strong></u><strong> </strong>🐈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a fearless cat and defend your village alone by crafting the perfect strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ <u><strong>Multiplayer - Co-op</strong></u><strong> </strong>🐈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with your friends through online play and work together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Running low on resources? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're running low on meat, borrowing a little wouldn’t hurt, would it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ <u><strong>Multiplayer - Devi</strong></u><strong>l </strong>🐈‍⬛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A devil disguised as a cat is hiding among your teammates! The devil cat sets traps and stuns plants, secretly sabotaging the team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you suspect someone, hold a vote and banish the devil cat from the village!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/e676bf2a0ec69f45b1f8450683f6b1f4.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/e676bf2a0ec69f45b1f8450683f6b1f4.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/753e155e0062ccf8a97ea40414e274ca.poster.avif?t=1754736393\" width=800 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/753e155e0062ccf8a97ea40414e274ca.webm?t=1754736393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your own plant towers to protect the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a selection of quirky, cat-friendly mutant plants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant, Care, and evolve them into powerful towers to keep your village safe!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/a1d8846cc9cfb38e113272ffa463ac32.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/a1d8846cc9cfb38e113272ffa463ac32.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through diverse and beautifully designed maps with varying difficulty levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize your way to victory and enjoy the satisfaction of clearing each map with your skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
