agraph\" >If you suspect someone, hold a vote and banish the devil cat from the village!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/e676bf2a0ec69f45b1f8450683f6b1f4.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/e676bf2a0ec69f45b1f8450683f6b1f4.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/753e155e0062ccf8a97ea40414e274ca.poster.avif?t=1754736393\" width=800 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/753e155e0062ccf8a97ea40414e274ca.webm?t=1754736393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your own plant towers to protect the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a selection of quirky, cat-friendly mutant plants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant, Care, and evolve them into powerful towers to keep your village safe!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/a1d8846cc9cfb38e113272ffa463ac32.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/a1d8846cc9cfb38e113272ffa463ac32.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through diverse and beautifully designed maps with varying difficulty levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize your way to victory and enjoy the satisfac